{"tid":863190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（估國家）兄弟玩嘢創Steve Jobs品牌 蘋果竟然輸官司無佢乎","createTime":"2018-10-15T11:52:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T12:28:20.000Z","uid":22675,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"d26ed95752383b79ef7953a01c275be36a7379c8","tid":863190,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:52:19.000Z","msg":"阿鬼<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.winandmac.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/steve-jobs-italy-fashion-brand.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2Fsteve-jobs-italy-fashion-brand.jpg&h=abd04d81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大陸經常有明明正牌，但被冒牌控告。早前，一對意大利的兄弟Vincenzo和Giacomo Barbato於2012年創立Steve Jobs品牌，原因之一是他們發覺蘋果竟然沒有為Steve Jobs申請商標註冊，所以理論上應該合法。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n當然，有關品牌成立後，很快就引起蘋果注意，蘋果更向歐盟相關商標註冊機構投訴，要求有關兄弟不要再用Steve Jobs作公司名稱。可惜的是，歐盟相關機構裁定意大利兄弟的Steve Jobs品牌中的J一字，雖然有被「咬一口」，但與蘋果本身的咬一口不同，<span style=\"color: red;\">始終「J」不是可以吃的東西</span>，結果意大利兄弟勝訴，可以繼續用Steve Jobs作品牌。<br />\n<br />\n不過，這對意大利兄弟的Steve Jobs只要是賣時裝潮流為主，例如Steve Jobs牛仔褲等。但他們早前接受傳媒訪問時，竟然説或許在未來，開始售賣電子科技產品。"},{"pid":"1ff070b181998845d83d098839ad1f5c0f193e97","tid":863190,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T11:52:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.winandmac.com/2018/10/steve-jobs-inc-italy-fashion-brand/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.winandmac.com%2F2018%2F10%2Fsteve-jobs-inc-italy-fashion-brand%2F&d=mXFPMEQdJt9qzdVrfsY5By7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=cf236d0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.winandmac.com/2018/10/steve-jobs-inc-italy-fashion-brand/</a>"},{"pid":"db59553c90886df0d692853a2942cfaa77540000","tid":863190,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T12:23:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3d3a22a2702965a808487ba8c60aa8619d4e408","tid":863190,"uid":10014,"like":2,"dislike":1,"scor